# bots.json: persisted bot roster    macros.json: saved macros
dashboard/data/
# generated map-render output, and the offline re-downloadable ViaVersion cache
framework/renders/
framework/tools/_viaversion_cache/

# -- logs ---------------------------------------------------------------------
*.log

# -- vendored resource pack: contains Mojang's copyrighted textures, which this
# project deliberately does NOT redistribute (see mcbot/resourcepack.py). Keep
# it local; each user supplies a pack they own. Remove this line to commit it.
framework/default_rpack.zip

